### WWDCQuotes ###

===========================================================================
DESCRIPTION:

This application accompanies the introductory and advanced text sessions for iOS. 
The sample is an iOS application which renders pages from well-known plays with
either the legacy string drawing functions or the new attributed drawing path.
It demonstrates the formatting of attributed strings, setting extended attributes,
background rendering, and showcases the advanced typographical features.

===========================================================================
BUILD REQUIREMENTS:

WWDC build of Xcode with the corresponding iOS SDK

===========================================================================
RUNTIME REQUIREMENTS:

WWDC 2012 iOS seed

===========================================================================
PACKAGING LIST:

Page.m: contains a representation of a page, as well as the code to format 
    and render it
MasterViewController.m: the main collection view
PageViewController.m: the detail view displaying the page's image
Pages/: this directory contains a number of excerpts already parsed into paragraphs (speaker/text)

